@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultTextAlignment left
skinparam ArrowColor #1F2937
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FEF3C7
skinparam NoteBorderColor #D97706
skinparam rectangle {
  FontColor #111827
  BorderColor #1F2937
}

title Auth Client Before: Email List + Admin Session Revoke

rectangle "createClient().auth.user.email.list()" as UserEmail #DBEAFE
rectangle "Auth Server Routes" as Routes #E5E7EB

UserEmail --> Routes : GET /email-list
note right of UserEmail
Single hard-coded route.
No contract-aware fallback to /email/list.
end note

rectangle "createClient().auth.admin.user.session.revoke(input)" as Revoke #FEE2E2
rectangle "Plural route payload builder" as Builder #FECACA
rectangle "/admin/revoke-user-sessions" as Plural #E5E7EB

Revoke --> Builder : list input
Builder --> Plural : POST { userId } OR { sessions: [...] }

note right of Builder
When multiple items had mixed userId values,
builder could emit { sessions: [...] }.
Server expects only { userId }.
end note
@enduml
